		"description": "<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-9d191353-7fff-60cf-8ce0-9a0b1498d34c\" dir=\"ltr\">You can release acidic sweat from your skin corrosive enough to dissolve non-magical material or burn creatures. You are immune to the acid you produce. The acid&rsquo;s potency is determined by the time spent producing the dose:</p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 67.1876px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 25.5357%;\"><col style=\"width: 74.4643%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\"><strong>Production time</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\"><strong>Dose potency</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">1 min</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">1 cubic inch of cloth or rope, 1 acid damage</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">5 min</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">1 cubic inch of leather or wood, 1d4 ongoing acid damage, 2 rounds</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">10 minutes</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">1 cubic inch of metal, 2d4 ongoing acid damage, 3 rounds</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;The sweat may be collected and stored in a glass vial but loses its potency and can no longer dissolve material after 24 hours.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Once you use this feature for a total of 10 minutes, you may not do so again until you complete a long rest.</p>",
